<DATELINE>
   KABUL
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
WARRING Sunni and Shia Moslem guerrilla factions took hundreds of civilians
hostage in Kabul with Afghanistan's new coalition government apparently
powerless to stop them, witnesses said yesterday, Reuter reports from Kabul.
The prisoners were singled out in the street at gunpoint on the basis of
