for the year to March 31, against Pounds 243,000 last time.
Second half profits increased from Pounds 51,000 to Pounds 205,000.
However, there were extraordinary charges of Pounds 242,000 (Pounds
302,000), relating to provisions on a property sale and an aborted
acquisition, resulting in a retained loss of Pounds 368,000 (Pounds 416,000)
