salary. Last month it was disclosed that Mr Leigh-Pemberton received a 28
per cent rise to Pounds 198,446 in 1991-92, but decided to waive all but 6
per cent of the increase.
A 17 per cent pay increase to Pounds 155,019 for the Governor in 1990
aroused controversy.
